node.title: Man charged following fatal crash
node.description: A man has been charged in relation to a fatal crash in Rotorua last month.
node.content:
["A man has been charged in relation to a fatal crash in Rotorua last month.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123RF\n
", "The single-vehicle crash on Te Ngae Rd occurred shortly after 11pm on 2 October.", "Police say one of one of the occupants later died in hospital.", "A 20-year-old Rotorua man has been charged with reckless driving causing death and refuding to provide a blood sample.", "He is due to appear in Rotorua District Court on 18 November."]
